text: Very good chicken wings. Crispy, flavourful but not too salty. Well balanced taste. Cabbage is crunchy and fresh. Bee Hoon is Al dente. ðŸ˜€

One of the tasty fried bee hoon and nasi lemak store at Bt Batok Ave 3 area. It is next to the vegetarian bee hoon store but they are able to have regular customers beside a strong competitor.

Won't hesitate to order from this store despite numerous similar stores there.
Both mee hoon and kway teow have some wok hei. Not overly flavorful. Chill could be better.
